1.1.4 to 1.1.5

- Move the OpenGL creation into gvxr-core
- Make sure it compiles on MS Window, Mac OS X, and GNU/Linux (desktop & supercomputer)

1.1.3 to 1.1.4

- Now fully support EGL context
- Compiles on SuperComputing Wales
- Successful run of unit tests on SuperComputing Wales


1.1.2 to 1.1.3

- Bug fixes
- Can load meshes from RAM
- Improve Numpy support


1.1.1 to 1.1.2

- Added files in root:
  - CHANGELOG (this file)
  - INSTALL.txt
  - LICENSE.txt
  - ORGANIZATION
  - README.md
  - VERSION.txt
- Added EGL support for when the computer has no screen
- Can read ASCII STL files
- Can load meshes from arrays
- Ease the installation from source
- Added a GUI
